---
title: Hearty Double Pork & Hidden Veggie Pie with Filo Pastry & Baby Spinach
description: Follow the scent of baked filo pastry pie to the dinner table. Cut a slice for yourself to enjoy the hidden veggies like carrot and
courgette, cooked in a tomato based pork filling. Go on, we know you want another slice, we sure do!

